>> It is strongly recommended that system designers do not connect the
>> AMD-8132 and devices that use extended
>> configuration space MMIO BARs (ex: HyperTransport-to-PCI ExpressÂ®
>> bridges) to the same processor
>> HyperTransport link.
>>
>> Fix Planned
